{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/13/itm_e344330877878891/index.md","canonical_url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.13669","category_id":"llm-agent","collected_at":"2026-06-13T02:35:32Z","content_hash":"83222a91d80369877f462f4a9771d844188200dbbee0a894723d58116329b3a7","evidence":[{"label":"arXiv abstract and submission date","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.13669"},{"label":"arXiv HTML full text","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/html/2606.13669v1"},{"label":"GraphAnything code repository","type":"url","url":"https://github.com/InternScience/GraphAnything"},{"label":"Scholar-KG dataset card","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/datasets/InternScience/Scholar-kg"},{"label":"Agents-K1 model card","type":"url","url":"https://huggingface.co/InternScience/Agents-K1"}],"external_id":"arxiv:2606.13669v1","fetched_at":"2026-06-13T02:35:32Z","fingerprint":"83222a91d80369877f462f4a9771d844188200dbbee0a894723d58116329b3a7","id":"itm_e344330877878891","item_id":"itm_e344330877878891","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-11T17:58:35Z","reading_minutes":28,"score":93,"sort_at":"2026-06-11T17:58:35Z","source_id":"arxiv","source_name":"arXiv","source_type":"manual","summary_zh":"Agents-K1 面向研究型大模型 Agent 的知识编排问题：现有 Agent 往往只临时检索摘要、chunk 或扁平 citation edge，缺少 claim、evidence、mechanism、method lineage 和可审计证据。论文提出三层系统：KG Layer 用 A-E 五模块 schema 从全文论文抽取元信息、显式实体、抽象实体、引用角色和实体关系；LLM Layer 用 Qwen3-4B-Instruct 初始化的 4B 信息抽取骨干，在 IEPile 与规则奖励下做 GRPO；CLI Layer 用 GraphAnything 统一 web search、多模态图检索和知识网络遍历。证据包括处理 246 万篇论文并发布约 100 万篇 Scholar-KG 子集、六学科抽取 AVG F1 约 79.07%-87.11%、FrontierScience-Research 中 GPT-5.2 overall 从 25.2% 到 39.4%、抽取骨干十个 NER/RE benchmark 平均 F1 0.5647。局限是关系抽取仍弱，CoNLL04 上 4B 训练模型 0.3181 明显落后 Qwen3-32B 的 0.4768；多项 reasoning 评估依赖 LLM-as-judge，长期图谱更新、污染防护和 Agent 写回治理仍待验证。","tags":["Agent","Knowledge Graph","GraphRAG","GRPO","Scientific Discovery","Information Extraction"],"title":"Agents-K1: Towards Agent-native Knowledge Orchestration","title_hash":"71edf765109b9e14a2343de6bc9b118b21c1f4d8ca02e68545f0369b49b6dfe5","type":"paper","updated_at":"2026-06-11T17:58:35Z","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.13669"}
{"analysis_markdown_path":"articles/2026/06/11/itm_498300817c8d0516/index.md","canonical_url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.13125","category_id":"llm-post-training","collected_at":"2026-06-13T02:34:21Z","content_hash":"bd9fb0f6083e19c32660910bd2f363bc30e97ebf694a0ea00cf613f607bbf629","evidence":[{"label":"arXiv abstract and metadata","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.13125"},{"label":"arXiv HTML full text","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/html/2606.13125v1"},{"label":"PDF full text","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2606.13125"},{"label":"Related work: DeepSeek-R1","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2501.12948"},{"label":"Related work: sharpening mechanism","type":"url","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.01951"}],"external_id":"arXiv:2606.13125","fetched_at":"2026-06-13T02:34:21Z","fingerprint":"bd9fb0f6083e19c32660910bd2f363bc30e97ebf694a0ea00cf613f607bbf629","id":"itm_498300817c8d0516","item_id":"itm_498300817c8d0516","language":"zh-CN","published_at":"2026-06-11T09:51:35Z","reading_minutes":18,"score":92,"sort_at":"2026-06-11T09:51:35Z","source_id":"arxiv","source_name":"arXiv","source_type":"manual","summary_zh":"这篇 2026-06-11 的论文用 Qwen2.5-1.5B-Instruct 上的有限域算术控制实验解释 RL 后训练如何提升推理：主要不是凭空发明新策略，而是通过 strategy selection 把题型路由到 SFT/预训练中已有的前向或后向策略，并通过 strategy improvement 在更难 RL 数据上打磨已有策略。关键证据是 Table 1：混合策略模型在 6-9 步验证集上的 pass@1 从 SFT 的 47.0% 提升到同难度 RL(2-5) 的 60.0%，再到更难 RL(6-9) 的 95.7%；B-only 模型在 inversion 上从 38.9% 到 96.0%，说明难度课程触发了策略改进。局限是任务为合成有限域算术、小模型和 outcome reward 设置，不能直接证明真实数学、代码或 Agent 后训练的全部规律。","tags":["LLM 后训练","RLVR","GRPO","推理模型","机制分析"],"title":"Select and Improve: Understanding the Mechanics of Post-Training for Reasoning","title_hash":"27961c2f311b6c1862f497e2d91edbaed1fc175e119dc1f0604ee4cfa86426c0","type":"paper","updated_at":"2026-06-11T09:51:35Z","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.13125"}
